                            <comment id="14717690" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Thu, 27 Aug 2015 22:47:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch select-init.diff copied from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BCEL-195&quot; title=&quot;addition of hashCode() to generic/Instruction.java breaks Targeters&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;BCEL-195&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;BCEL-195&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This performs as much initialisation as possible before allowing the partially constructed object to escape.&lt;/p&gt;

